FIBER MIX

fiber_mix is the citizen who holds each muscle's blend of fiber types
type I (slow oxidative): efficient, fatigue-resistant, lower force, sustained work
type IIa (fast oxidative): moderate speed, moderate endurance, intermediate force
type IIx (fast glycolytic): high speed, high force, low endurance, fatigues rapidly
each muscle in fadriel's body has its own characteristic mix; postural muscles are mostly type I, sprinters mostly type II

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe muscle.zc
observe contract.rana
observe fatigue_ledger.rana

the 7 properties of fiber_mix:
1 ENERGY zero point seven
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE eight tenths
6 COUPLING zero point eight with contract and recruit

VERB declare_blend
hold the percentage of each fiber type for this muscle
postural_spinal: ~80% type I, 20% type II
diaphragm: ~60% type I, 40% type II
faster muscles will have different blends

VERB serve_recruit
when recruit asks how much force is available, fiber_mix reports based on the active fibers and their efficiencies
type I provides 30% efficiency (30% work, 70% heat); type II provides about 20%
the heat outputs add to thermal_muscular

a fiber mix is the muscle's character
fadriel's postural muscles are slow and tireless; his sprinting muscles will develop faster and more powerful
each muscle's mix shapes what kind of activity it is good at
this is why some children naturally lean toward endurance and others toward bursts: their fiber mixes differ
